    <b>Some of the worst impacts include:</b>
    <li>Melting of Ice Caps in Antarctica due to global warming.</li>
    <li>The average temperature of Earth rising by about 1¬∞ Celsius.</li>
    <li>
      The amount of CO<sub>2</sub> increasing in the atmosphere, trapping more
      sunlight.
    </li>
    <li>
      Rise in sea-level, increasing the chances of tsunamis and earthquakes. üò¨
